<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Six fragments, none joining, apparently from the same <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">panel</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.03-0.04</measure>) whose back survives. No edges, except for d, which has an upper edge with clamp hole above. a: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.145</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.10</measure>; b: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.19</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.13</measure>; c: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.13</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height"><measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.12</measure></measure>; d: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.23</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.18</measure>; e: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.12</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.10</measure>; f: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.25</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.235</measure>.
</p>
</div>
